graph LR
    Kueue[Kueue Operator<br/>Job Queueing System]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Kueue -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.22+<br/>Target platform]
    Kueue -->|framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.17.3<br/>Kubernetes controller framework]
    Kueue -->|certificates| CertController[cert-controller v0.10.1<br/>Webhook TLS cert management]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Kueue -.->|monitoring| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>Optional PodMonitor support]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies (Job Framework Integration)
    Kueue -->|queues training jobs| TrainingOp[Kubeflow Training Operator<br/>TFJob, PyTorchJob, MPIJob, MXJob,<br/>PaddleJob, XGBoostJob]
    Kueue -->|queues inference| KServe[KServe<br/>Inference serving workloads]
    Kueue -->|queues Ray workloads| RayOp[Ray Operator<br/>RayJob, RayCluster]

    %% Integration Points
    Kueue -->|watches CRDs| JobSet[JobSet<br/>jobset.x-k8s.io]
    Kueue -->|watches jobs| BatchJobs[Kubernetes Batch Jobs<br/>batch/v1]

    %% External Services
    Kueue -->|creates requests| ClusterAutoscaler[Cluster Autoscaler<br/>ProvisioningRequest API]
    Kueue -->|metrics scraping| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics collection]

    %% API Server (central dependency)
    Kueue -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+]
    TrainingOp -->|CRDs| K8sAPI
    RayOp -->|CRDs| K8sAPI
    KServe -.->|CRDs| K8sAPI
    JobSet -->|CRDs| K8sAPI
    BatchJobs -->|CRDs| K8sAPI
    ClusterAutoscaler -->|watches| K8sAPI
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| Kueue

    %% Styling
    style Kueue fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies (gray)
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style CertController fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style PrometheusOp fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style K8sAPI fill:#666,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies (green)
    style TrainingOp fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style RayOp fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000

    %% Job frameworks (light green)
    style JobSet fill:#a8e6a1,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style BatchJobs fill:#a8e6a1,stroke:#333,color:#000

    %% External services (orange)
    style ClusterAutoscaler fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style Prometheus fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#000

    %% Link styling
    linkStyle 0,1,2 stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    linkStyle 3 stroke:#999,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    linkStyle 4,5,6 stroke:#7ed321,stroke-width:3px
